<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Order Confirmed</title>
  <style>
    body { margin: 0; padding: 0; background: #f4f6f9; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif; color: #333; }
    .wrapper { width: 100%; background: #f4f6f9; padding: 40px 0; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 10px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }
    .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); padding: 40px 40px 30px; text-align: center; }
    .header h1 { color: #ffffff; margin: 0; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.5px; }
    .header p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); margin: 8px 0 0; font-size: 15px; }
    .checkmark { font-size: 48px; display: block; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .body { padding: 36px 40px; }
    .greeting { font-size: 16px; color: #444; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.5; }
    .info-card { background: #f8f9fc; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px 24px; margin-bottom: 28px; border-left: 4px solid #667eea; }
    .info-card p { margin: 4px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #555; }
    .info-card strong { color: #222; }
    table.items { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    table.items th { background: #f0f2f7; text-align: left; padding: 10px 12px; font-size: 12px; color: #666; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; }
    table.items td { padding: 10px 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; font-size: 14px; color: #444; }
    table.items tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
    .total-row td { font-weight: 700; font-size: 16px; color: #222; padding-top: 14px; border-top: 2px solid #e0e0e0; }
    .cta { text-align: center; margin: 32px 0; }
    .btn { display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; padding: 14px 36px; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.3px; }
    .footer { background: #f8f9fc; padding: 24px 40px; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid #eee; }
    .footer p { font-size: 12px; color: #999; margin: 4px 0; line-height: 1.5; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <span class="checkmark">âœ…</span>
        <h1>Order Confirmed!</h1>
        <p>Your order has been received and is being processed.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="body">
        <p class="greeting">Hi <strong>{{name}}</strong>,<br />Thank you for your order! We're getting everything ready for you.</p>

        <div class="info-card">
          <p><strong>Order Number:</strong> #{{orderNumber}}</p>
          <p><strong>Order ID:</strong> {{orderId}}</p>
        </div>

        <table class="items">
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>Item</th>
              <th>Qty</th>
              <th>Price</th>
              <th>Subtotal</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            {{#each items}}
            <tr>
              <td>{{this.productName}}</td>
              <td>{{this.quantity}}</td>
              <td>{{../currency}} {{this.price}}</td>
              <td>{{../currency}} {{this.subtotal}}</td>
            </tr>
            {{/each}}
          </tbody>
          <tfoot>
            <tr class="total-row">
              <td colspan="3">Total</td>
              <td>{{currency}} {{total}}</td>
            </tr>
          </tfoot>
        </table>

        <div class="cta">
          <a href="{{trackingUrl}}" class="btn">View Your Order</a>
        </div>

        <p style="font-size:14px;color:#666;line-height:1.6;">
          We'll notify you when your order ships. If you have any questions, reply to this email or visit our support centre.
        </p>
        <p style="font-size:14px;color:#666;">Best regards,<br /><strong>The MarketX Team</strong></p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>You received this email because you placed an order on MarketX.</p>
        <p>&copy; {{year}} MarketX Inc. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
